     Future major version upgrades require a new perpetual purchase or an
     active annual subscription at the time of upgrade.

Rights granted under Indie Pro:

   - Commercial use in unlimited products and projects
   - Use in games, SaaS, mobile apps, web applications, client work
   - Attribution is OPTIONAL — no credit required
   - Email support (response within 5 business days)
   - All Software updates within the licensed major version
   - Covers a single legal entity (individual or incorporated company)
