================================================================================
WHAT IS INCLUDED IN ALL PAID LICENSES (TIERS 1–3)
================================================================================

   - ChiptuneSynth v3+ — 8-track synthesis engine
   - 170+ instrument presets via ChiptuneSoundFont
   - Per-track effects chain: distortion, chorus, delay, reverb, bitcrusher
   - Mixer console: pan, 3-band EQ, per-track compressor, solo/mute
   - Master brick-wall limiter
   - Arpeggiator: BPM-synced, multi-octave, 4 modes
   - Full Web MIDI: velocity, CC, pitch bend, mod wheel
   - CDN-hosted builds: cdn.8binami.com/chiptune-synth/
   - All updates within the licensed major version
   - Access to the 8BitForge interactive demo and full documentation


================================================================================
LICENSE VERIFICATION & ENFORCEMENT
================================================================================

1. SELF-REPORTING. Revenue tiers operate on an honor system. 8Binami reserves
   the right to request reasonable revenue verification (e.g., platform
   dashboards, financial filings) for accounts suspected of tier
   misrepresentation.

2. AUDIT RIGHT. 8Binami may audit compliance with 7 days written notice,
   once per calendar year per licensee. Audits are conducted via document
   review; no access to internal systems is required.

3. GRACE PERIOD. Licensees have 30 days from the date their revenue exceeds
   their current tier to upgrade. No retroactive fees are charged within
   the grace period if the licensee upgrades within this window.

4. TERMINATION. 8Binami may terminate any license immediately and without
   refund upon:
      - Material breach of this license
      - Attempted reverse engineering of the Software
      - Persistent non-payment of license fees after 30-day notice
      - Deliberate misrepresentation of revenue tier

   Upon termination, the licensee must cease all use of the Software and
   remove it from all active products within 30 days.

5. LICENSE TRANSFER. Licenses are not transferable to a different legal
   entity (e.g., upon acquisition or merger) without prior written consent
   from 8Binami. Transfer requests will be evaluated within 15 business days.

6. REFUND POLICY. Annual licenses are refundable within 14 days of purchase
   if the Software has not been used in a released product. Perpetual
   licenses are non-refundable after 30 days.


